I'm currently trying to find a role as a [ROLE TITLE] and given your extensive experience in the field, I would really value your advice on how to break into the industry.

A bit about me:
- [Relevant accomplishment]
- [Relevant accomplishment]
- [Relevant accomplishment]

I'd love to ask you about your insights on [INDUSTRY, JOB, COMPANY]. Would you be available for a short 20 minute chat on [SPECIFIC DATE/TIME]? It would be immensely valuable for me.

Looking forward to hearing from you!

All the best,
[YOUR NAME]
[JOB TITLE]
[LINKEDIN URL]`,
    example: `Hi Kai,

I hope you're having a good week so far! My name is Imani and I came across your profile a while ago as a result of searching for the top digital marketing agencies in Toronto. I've got to say, after taking a look at your personal website your experience speaks for itself!

I'm a relative newcomer to Toronto, and have been on the hunt for digital marketing roles. Seeing as you're someone with a lot of experience in this field, I wanted to get in touch.

A bit about me:

- A few months ago, I launched a google campaign that saw an 8x increase in conversion rates, which led to the company having its best months in online sales back to back.
- This year, I wrote and designed over 20 email campaigns that increased open rates by 10% (avg) and increased the CTR by 11% (avg)
- In the last 6 months, I've redesigned over 20 webpages to improve their SEO and/or optimize them for conversions.

I'd love the opportunity to hop on a short call and learn a bit more about the marketing landscape here in Toronto and any insights you might be willing to share.

Would you be available for a short 20 minute chat on Monday, December 9, at 11am? If not I'm happy to work around your schedule.

Looking forward to hearing from you!

All the best,
Imani Diaz
Marketing Manager
